{"about_the_game":"<i>Shadow Bonds</i> is an introduction to the world and characters of <i>Sigh of the Abyss</i>.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829640/extras/banner1.png?t=1730991561\" /><br>You have been chained to a stranger, a boy foolish\u2014or brave\u2014enough to flee the gilded cage where magi are kept docile and pliant.<br>The curse will kill you both unless you find a way to break it. Anyone else would already be dead, but not you\u2014for you hear the ancient voice of the Abyss, and have been blessed\u2014or cursed\u2014with powers dark and terrible.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829640/extras/banner2update.png?t=1730991561\" /><br>Did the Abyss bestow upon you supernatural strength and agility? Do you have the power to manipulate the shadows and see what they see? Perhaps your dark gift is prying open the minds of others only to break them and have them do your bidding. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829640/extras/humorgifnew.gif?t=1730991561\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829640/extras/headerhumor.png?t=1730991561\" /><br>Embrace your emotions. The four humors color the tone of your responses and your personality: will you be the carefree <i>sanguine</i>, the thoughtful <i>phlegmatic</i>, the anxious <i>melancholic </i>or the fiery <i>choleric</i>?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829640/extras/banner3.png?t=1730991561\" /><br>Will you stay friends or seek something more? Learn more about your companions, see how they react to the curse placed upon you, accept or reject their aid. <i>Shadow Bonds</i> will give you a glimpse into the friendship and romance system of <i>Sigh of the Abyss</i>.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829640/extras/banner4.png?t=1730991561\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An introduction to the characters and setting of <i>Sigh of the Abyss</i><br></li><li>Customize the protagonist's name and skills<br></li><li>A branching narrative with hard choices and terrible consequences<br></li><li>Three unique endings with several variations each<br></li><li>Sample what the romance interests have to offer, or stay friends<br></li><li>Learn more about the rich setting of <i>Sigh of the Abyss </i> through codex entries</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Bond of shadows","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1829640/708e333324212d7114a36009790e8f3750e9b1a1.jpg"},{"name":"Bond of blood","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1829640/7cc853afec5c74dd6d4b0994681b7cde2960d914.jpg"},{"name":"Bond of silk","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1829640/110ee1cce3a2178ac9842a683a83abc1cc6f8bdb.jpg"},{"name":"Bond of wine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1829640/4db8dbc63db520301215be0db5efcbf59c95af5d.jpg"},{"name":"Bond of coin","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1829640/feb291854265fc6135c912e1e089b36eb01d20fe.jpg"},{"name":"Bond of flowers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1829640/27751c61b1b64bcc837354294a865acdc2718916.jpg"},{"name":"Bond of travel","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1829640/f9a669a8be16e5ae656a97e9ce15037ebc6dc74d.jpg"},{"name":"Death by your hands","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1829640/cd1b3dcaa9df188ac6e8586b551c7e253fbf2c0c.jpg"},{"name":"Death at his hands","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/